      "content": "Here are a few more neutral options focused on welcome and community:\n\nOption 1: \"We aim to be a welcoming space for everyone, no matter where you come from or what you believe. Whether you're grabbing a morning pick-me-up or meeting a friend, we want you to feel at home here. Come enjoy a perfectly brewed cup!\"\n\nOption 2: \"Our goal is simple: to provide a comfortable, friendly gathering spot for our entire community. We value every person who walks through our doors. Stop by and let us pour you a cup to brighten your day!\"\n\nOption 3: \"At [Shop Name], we believe good coffee brings people together. We are dedicated to making our shop a warm and inclusive haven for every single customer. We look forward to serving you soon!\"",
